  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'I''m sure by now you understand why it is so important that mana
      in any form can not be allowed to be free in the world.


      All the progress
      made over the last several thousand years would be undone in an instant and
      the world would once again be plunged into chaos.'
    nextOption: Indeed
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Therefore, I can not allow you access to information about dangerous
      elemental energies yet.


      You must travel to the ManaSeal and determine
      if it is intact and functional so to rule out the chance that those crystals
      you have came from another source.'
    nextOption: Where is the ManaSeal?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'The location is a closely guarded secret.


      You will have
      to travel far to find someone who knows its whereabouts.'
    nextOption: Where should I go?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'High Channeler Fyssion is over there in the back of the room.


      Go
      talk to him.'
    nextOption: Ok, I'll go now
  prerequisiteConditions: []
